// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2290 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: a9c2636e-8da5-52a8-919d-b06910010dbd

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:1*" or process.executable like~ "*chainguard:*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
